{"tid":861432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得物以類聚真係好啱？","createTime":"2018-10-14T06:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T06:50:35.000Z","uid":157897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66e67916d84f82acff6b6739dc8d6693a4615581","tid":861432,"uid":157897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:35:25.000Z","msg":"其實女神身邊真係好多女神friend<br />\n男神身邊又係好多男神friend<br />\n有幾可會見到有個女神post自己同個豬扒合照？又或者男神身邊有個毒L？<br />\n可能有嘅 但係一定好少先<br />\n<br />\n然後如果有個女神同豬扒係由細識到大更加容易無friend做<br />\n因為一個永遠都受大家喜愛 一個就成日望住佢既光芒 其實都好殘忍 邊會有人真係無妒忌心？雖然知道我無資格去傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己就係望住人地個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後個女神friend已經去左女神個堆 又yo得又多friend 我繼續做豬扒同毒L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265d125fc8595d28b576a131b421320a31df5985","tid":861432,"uid":186208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"見過有好多靚女旁邊都有個豬西密友"},{"pid":"f93a89162e50bf40189a21bbcb4f3743a21833a8","tid":861432,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"通常男神身邊都有個肥仔笑彈"},{"pid":"ea5b0ac8dc9ae49c500325611090e2d8138970a6","tid":861432,"uid":25062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265d125fc8595d28b576a131b421320a31df5985","tid":861432,"uid":186208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"見過有好多靚女旁邊都有個豬西密友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:44:13.000Z","msg":"單純因爲有件豬西你先覺得靚，本質上唔靚唔係女神"},{"pid":"7605b61c3ddb8f48bea3fd89dd8cc2345ac3f6be","tid":861432,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"睇完第一段已經唔洗睇<br />\n靚女張張合照都係公開處刑架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}